%% Diagram: Query cache state machine
%% Type: state
%%{init: {'htmlLabels': false}}%%
stateDiagram-v2
    [*] --> Pending: useQuery mounts\nno cache entry
    Pending --> Fresh: fetch resolves\nstore data + timestamp
    Fresh --> Stale: age > staleTime
    Stale --> Refetching: trigger\n(focus / mount / interval)
    Refetching --> Fresh: 200 OK
    Refetching --> Stale: error\n(retry policy decides)
    Fresh --> Inactive: last subscriber unmounts
    Stale --> Inactive: last subscriber unmounts
    Inactive --> Fresh: subscriber mounts\nbefore gcTime
    Inactive --> Stale: subscriber mounts\nafter staleTime
    Inactive --> [*]: gcTime elapsed\nentry evicted

    classDef live fill:#1F6E68,stroke:#155752,color:#ffffff
    classDef warn fill:#8B5E15,stroke:#6E4810,color:#ffffff
    classDef cold fill:#5A5A5A,stroke:#3D3D3D,color:#ffffff
    class Fresh live
    class Stale,Refetching warn
    class Inactive cold
